data.description: Do not judge the book by it's cover! This home brings back all the World Class Charm of yesterday year with all of the modern conveniences of today! Many upgrades thru out the years. Heater, Water Heater & windows are newer. Six Fireplaces with three of them operational. Two separate stairs leading to two separate attics. More than half of the property is tillable. Plenty of hunting opportunities. Man made pond. Take a personal tour and see what awaits you!
